    "rationale": "Model deemed sufficiently credible for COU1. All verification goals achieved at or above target gradation levels. Validation comparison at all 5 operating conditions shows hemolysis index below CPB predicate threshold (RH < 1). No formal CFD uncertainty quantification performed for COU1 (addressed by W-AL-01 weakener).",
